{"tid":1032601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：大灣區執教供教師多一個選擇","createTime":"2019-02-22T13:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T14:52:50.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cb15712a35c61733bc549f3f6ee19c70603d18e5","tid":1032601,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】粵港澳大灣區規劃綱要提出，研究開放港澳教師到廣東考取資格並任教。教育局局長楊潤雄表示，正跟內地商討細節。他承認香港教師薪酬較高，安排是為有志在內地執教的教師提供多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府曾探討本港辦學團體到大灣區辦香港課程的學校，讓日後到大灣區工作的港人的子女入讀，以便銜接本地課程，楊潤雄指，仍跟內地政府及本港的辦學團體商討政策及資源上的配合。"},{"pid":"5e42a3fbe4c6d86ebe71c47a9d28e323a82406ee","tid":1032601,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/52779861_2266231580370864_3306668262896435200_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=221854719bcf75b17f1280943976ddb1&amp;oe=5CF09B7C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F52779861_2266231580370864_3306668262896435200_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D221854719bcf75b17f1280943976ddb1%26oe%3D5CF09B7C&h=39fd75cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a8b527900f3b04b1ff1c1f0da08d18edc7db658","tid":1032601,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba497d5ea46d10b0f8b6e4f734815aaa94316ae","tid":1032601,"uid":18016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"上去有得打小朋友 爽咁多  唔洗日日上網吐苦水"},{"pid":"9af7e87987cc97f60c4dcb58e4253b4a87bdd50f","tid":1032601,"uid":90863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"我地港獨派果然行前過人好撚多步"},{"pid":"3188a089007cd3601bac8099905a59b853dcaa92","tid":1032601,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T13:50:00.00